{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a really-- a rough, brutal guy-- guy, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He beat us up-- and specially me, because he knew who-- who-- who I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then this-- this kind of aggravation, and then finally, my-- I had my uncle, my brother-- my mother's brother, older brother, who came to Canada-- immigrated to Canada in 1927, took up a homestead in northern Alberta, so- so he was out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then my father and mother decided, well, the best way for us to leave the country, because then-- then-- there was a sort of a [INAUDIBLE] movement, you see, to boycott me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they had to come to him, because he was the only-- only harness maker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was--he was making all good, as I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was able to send two of his children to pub-- to high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's not-- it wasn't an escape, but as- but as I said, my father was under such-- such pressure, and the- and the- and the village, village, uh, the village-- not-- not the clerk.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there is not a name in English-- who-- who-- was the head of the--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- well, not-- not-- not the mayor, which it has another, but it's like-- like the mayor in the- in the cities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the- he was the head of the-- head of the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was- he was also an escapee from-- from-- from-- Transyl-- from Romania.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So these people hated-- hated everybody, because the Romanian army was the main force-- main force, which was used by [NON-ENGLISH] to suppress the revolution.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So did everything added together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- and that all-- all this burden was-- was on-- on my father, until he felt we had enough.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
